              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(a Semitic idiom, literally: sons of men) human beings (equivalent in denotative meaning to {L:ἄνθρωπος&lt;SDBG:ἄνθρωπος:000000&gt;}[a], {D:9.1})</DefinitionShort>
